This must be known by the representatives of the UOHS more than well, but apparently their interests elsewhere.
It goes when no one looks
Without notice, however, the operation of some pseudovirtual operators, which there are now several in Czech mobile networks.
They are companies issuing their own pricelists of mobile phone services, but they are only partially public.
