"If there were cases that you are talking about, there could be a breach of the contractual terms that we would deal with and could result in the termination of cooperation with the company," she replied to our question about this issue, Martin Kemrová.
However, it is unlikely that a similar activity would not be brought to responsible people from mobile operators.
